    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Re owners: IMO this should work based on current selection.  Select should by default only select the players actors, it would be weird and distracting to select all your allies' units when trying to command your forces ingame.  If the selection already contains other player's actors then those players should also be included in the expanded selection."
